      both currencies:<br>
      Total:<br>
      $1.50 USD<br>
      0.015 BTC<br>
      Bob says, “That’s one-dollar-fifty, or fifteen millibits.”<br>
      Bob’s point-of-sale system will also automatically create a special QR
